PhoneCommentForm is a Form
    title is "BudgetChangeRequestLineComment"
    Layout
        single column
            FinanceEnterpriseGroup
                display as text
            BudgetChangeOrder
                label is "ChangeRequest"
                display as text
            BudgetChangeOrderLine
                label is "ChangeRequestLine"
                display as text
            Subject
            Comment
                use text area of 3 lines
            From
            visible when (HasComment)
                CommentDate
                    display as text
        paragraph
            Attachment
                compact format
            visible when (HasAttachment)
                button of "View"
                    view Attachment.File
                    display as link
